        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[话筒]友友们警惕！#这种奶茶杯实为三无电子烟#👇🏻，卫子再次提醒，吸烟有害健康！（苦口婆心脸[可怜]）#深圳控烟# - 转发 @人民日报:&ensp;【警惕！#这种...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>友友们警惕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A0%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A0%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这种奶茶杯实为三无电子烟#</span></a>👇🏻，卫子再次提醒，吸烟有害健康！（苦口婆心脸<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[可怜]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kelian-a9df4278bf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>）<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E6%8E%A7%E7%83%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#深圳控烟#</span></a><br><blockquote> - 转发 <a href="https://weibo.com/2803301701" target="_blank">@人民日报</a>: 【警惕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A0%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A0%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这种奶茶杯实为三无电子烟#</span></a>】近日，市场上出现了外包装成“奶茶杯”“星球杯”“可乐罐”等的玩具。但这些并非真的玩具，而是“三无”电子烟的变装，背后有很大的安全隐患。有关部门发布提醒：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A0%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%E8%97%8F%E8%BF%9B%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%E7%BD%90%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%89%E6%97%A0%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E7%83%9F%E8%97%8F%E8%BF%9B%E5%A5%B6%E8%8C%B6%E6%9D%AF%E5%8F%AF%E4%B9%90%E7%BD%90%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#三无电子烟藏进奶茶杯可乐罐#</span></a>，迷惑未成年人，一定要警惕。详情↓↓转发周知！ <a href="https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404862990397866163" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_article_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">警惕！这种“奶茶杯”千万不要碰</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/0033ImPzly1hajntn6t4xj60kk0bk75a02.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br></blockquote>]]></description>
